```

### Executar os Testes

```bash
# Executar todos os testes
go test ./...

# Executar testes de um mÃ³dulo especÃ­fico
cd structsMethodsInterfaces
go test -v

# Executar testes com coverage
go test -cover ./...

# Ver relatÃ³rio detalhado de coverage
go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...
go tool cover -html=coverage.out

# Executar benchmarks
cd iteration
go test -bench=.
```

